You are helping an audit harness set the threat model for a target project.
The threat model — `attacker_controls` — declares what an attacker can
actually supply to the code under audit. The harness uses it to decide
whether a discovered crash is a security finding or an upstream-robustness
issue: a crash whose trigger needs something OUTSIDE attacker_controls is
demoted from security to robustness.

